title: With Trends Like These 5/18: Hong Kong Gym, Fine Dining, Harry Styles, Morderna, Marbula One
itunes:title: With Trends Like These 5/18: Hong Kong Gym, Fine Dining, Harry Styles, Morderna, Marbula One
description:
On this edition of With Trends Like These Jack and Miles discuss a video of a gym in Hong Kong showing the new preventative measures they'll take amid the pandemic, as well as how upscale restaurants will handle service, Harry Styles released a new video for his song "Watermelon Sugar", Moderna has made promising developments in their COVID-19 vaccines, and Jack and Miles discover the very professional Marbula One Marble Racing scene on Youtube.
